## ğŸ§  OOP Concepts Implemented

| Concept | Usage in Project |
|--------|-----------------|
| **Class & Object** | Represent Bank Accounts and operations |
| **Constructors** | Initialize new account objects |
| **Inheritance** | SavingsAccount and CheckingAccount extend Base Account class |
| **Method Overriding** | Different withdrawal/interest logic for each account type |
| **Encapsulation** | Private data members with controlled access |
| **Polymorphism** | Same method name performing different behaviors |
| **Exception Handling** | Handles insufficient balance errors |

